{"tid":424923,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"考車路試肥佬好灰","createTime":"2017-10-05T08:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T03:31:31.000Z","uid":152016,"like":3,"dislike":101,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"85701e0d569578c68ba1f5c680b270054d4079b9","tid":424923,"uid":152016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:18:41.000Z","msg":"小弟跟駕院學車，中期路試分開考，而且一早就知考油塘，所以一開始都唔太緊張。學車個陣一直都無咩大問題，最後個幾堂自問揸得極穩，師傅都話揸得唔錯。到考個朝（我考朝早）都唔算好緊張，只係好似放榜咁。試車個陣個師傅仲同我講中秋考牌，一生難忘，唉，考到就係，而家炒左直頭想跳樓身亡。入返正題，臨考前係架車到等考官都唔算緊張，不過考官一黎就比佢個氣場影響，開始驚。跟住終於開車啦，我好似平時咁跟足步驟望哂無車先揸出去，點知一踩油門架車beep beep beep 咁響，原來唔記得放手制。考官即刻話＂你未放手制啊，放左先啦，唔使緊張，考試繼續。＂我立時方寸大亂，唸住cut 條右線再行，明明cut 之前望左無車，一踩油門就比考官brake 停左，話＂條線有車啊，人地有優先權架。＂一望又真係有架車係到。結果，我未出嘉榮街（揸未夠10秒）就知肥左。跟住個考官話＂好，考試繼續。＂我心唸＂可唔可以唔繼續，而家比我落車返屋企搶快期。＂但係最後我都死死氣咁揸埋落去，<br />\n只係成程好無隱，明知炒左都仲要揸。最後出成績毫無懸念，比人剔左3個嚴重（1. 物體前急速扭軑切入，2. 考官作出行動，3. 腳制控制不當）btw, 第1同第3都唔係好知衰乜，我中1號線，唔使點過死車，應該唔會衰物體前急速扭軑切入，腳制我就真係唔知做乜。<br />\n唉，明明學車個陣都未試過咁樣，考個陣就另一回事，咁樣補多幾多個鐘都無用。<br />\n<br />\n利申：自動波都炒想死"},{"pid":"67a1536f7d21527694f30dd4190fec35b77cd32c","tid":424923,"uid":3122,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:20:10.000Z","msg":"睇完頭七隻字都知咩事"},{"pid":"32d3b247be4593a534213db3e24200f3768ef958","tid":424923,"uid":152016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完頭七隻字都知咩事</blockquote><br />\n點解咁講"},{"pid":"a1a8619e86fd0f07b57d955671e8c3af8b3b6e6c","tid":424923,"uid":28245,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"駕院邊有油堂 去觀駕就最on9<br />\n<br />\n價錢同港駕差唔多但又買唔到條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1341418494dc554141dd86d847ef067ff149c2e","tid":424923,"uid":11067,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:22:45.000Z","msg":"少一個炸彈"},{"pid":"a4b906819d9faa463a2f79a1fa63d70d706bc7e6","tid":424923,"uid":98172,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T08:29:54.000Z","msg":"肥佬真係好小事, 你又唔係考5,6次都唔得<br />\n前年我肥左2次先考到, 而家已經日日渣車番工收工."},{"pid":"9b2b7733fe8db0785bd96d5d8195fed4a705df13","tid":424923,"uid":128613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"寧願學好佢都啥好做炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f443c4669a5c358323cfea790fdc1f69e5a083","tid":424923,"uid":128613,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧願學好佢都唔好做炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ced14316b096470a7f7c85af44069c9ebc577549","tid":424923,"uid":11704,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"有無人可以解釋下點解考車對人咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d7a9bea3a9cc184a62fcd06552bf5e6c7a775d","tid":424923,"uid":117628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:37:13.000Z","msg":"乜駕院都會肥架咩？"},{"pid":"9b627d824129d8906aa14446bab1926d78f84275","tid":424923,"uid":152016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜駕院都會肥架咩？</blockquote><br />\n合格率同出面差唔多"},{"pid":"c8acb9d9d28b293bd1ffa18ec62ba2ee2dac8b77","tid":424923,"uid":35408,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自動波都肥"},{"pid":"0779318008d989ccbfe289686aebb24c3bd6fe8d","tid":424923,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自動波都肥</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dc3b0cc6331b8743404e4c07340303b349311f","tid":424923,"uid":37505,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:06:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人可以解釋下點解考車對人咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考前就真係好大壓力<br />\n考完就真係唔明壓力從何而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7819fc511c317b993f74dcc22fad244894f2e588","tid":424923,"uid":72,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜駕院都會肥架咩？</blockquote><br />\n合格率同出面差唔多</blockquote><br />\n之前睇駕院30幾% 出面20幾%<br />\n<br />\nBtw 我之前都係考油塘，如果考10點打後啲時間真係只可以祈禱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太多死車，啲人又亂過馬路亂揸車"},{"pid":"ce2c0779d74a68f15d97f7c08ad268ade42538e4","tid":424923,"uid":147454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T10:11:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有無人可以解釋下點解考車對人咁大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n考前就真係好大壓力<br />\n考完就真係唔明壓力從何而來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肥一次就跌4-5 千"},{"pid":"8095591cf0d746e2104e30848132cc7f5ada9367","tid":424923,"uid":20570,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"巴打我同你情況一樣 到考個時一做錯少少野 就好騰雞 最後仲肥埋 成個星期無哂心情 但係諗諗其實肥左有咩所謂 知道自己邊到錯 下次再做好去 好過一take pass左之後出去做馬路炸彈 加油巴打 支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8a524784c7553ae6583ab6c8745939440e2c1f","tid":424923,"uid":19867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:50:20.000Z","msg":"廢牌都肥 廢撚到"},{"pid":"d683ab6bd7dc70ce89d47ae8197e73ac489a089d","tid":424923,"uid":57462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"我考天光道 泊車都死左2次火<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後一take pass"},{"pid":"b0c41400e8833088adcf4c5144a6a61713c3b699","tid":424923,"uid":17658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:42:05.000Z","msg":"第一次考 腳都震埋 未出試場已經死火<br />\n第二次已經輕鬆面對"},{"pid":"6d1983c7b98836520997e8126d7201be552b96f4","tid":424923,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"觀駕同街外師傅冇分別，一D優勢都冇。仲以為你講香港駕駛學院。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8779ea8d419e5d839e1afb19cc3c08af4bde9a33","tid":424923,"uid":126017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"死火之後抱住肥硬心態輕鬆揸埋落去<br />\n<br />\n點知1 take pass"},{"pid":"37fd7589c02a80577d1dc46a662ae5744f21b7bc","tid":424923,"uid":132750,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T06:12:45.000Z","msg":"講真 一世人流流長 <br />\n又點會樣樣野都無風無浪<br />\n再排期補鐘考過囉<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"38ec97965111c22aa90ae20bdb159ec2ed9e3d5a","tid":424923,"uid":117183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:01:51.000Z","msg":"廢牌都肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60d2a8edf643905c767709f9fd7906c51fdbff4","tid":424923,"uid":132709,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:12:05.000Z","msg":"如果連考車的環境都處理唔店，他日你只會成為另一個路面炸彈。<br />\n比心機操多次幾次車再去考 la"},{"pid":"10b17720bb3540ad1fc6644a16ee0071df4db6aa","tid":424923,"uid":5583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T07:21:13.000Z","msg":"真心 肥左咪考過囉 <br />\n當多個經驗 今次知衰啲咩 下次咪唔會再犯<br />\n最起碼唔係道路炸彈先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都肥左冇望線 <br />\n<br />\n樓主加油 共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef80084c79cea380332728a454ad58d1b298d9f","tid":424923,"uid":64850,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:25:50.000Z","msg":"我咪又係肥油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個tick咋屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我衰同人揮手呀 我仲想死呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5dabc5f98e6b0514a72008ba688ae22cfaae5c","tid":424923,"uid":64850,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:32:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我咪又係肥油塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個tick咋屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我衰同人揮手呀 我仲想死呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我想講既係 肥左係改變唔到既事實<br />\n塞翁失馬 焉知非福<br />\n你有三個大剔 比你出到街反而更危險<br />\n今次肥你 希望你知道自己衰乜<br />\n同渣車都需要有個大心臟 冷靜面對路面情況<br />\n加油啦我都係過來人 我肥得仲dum心口過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6022f4a9649ad21f984d4f0ad64eaa95f76cbef","tid":424923,"uid":623,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:46:09.000Z","msg":"廢牌都肥就唔好再考啦ok?"},{"pid":"e1d92a89cbca6c4d8ac6a6e394d33be52acf3fb8","tid":424923,"uid":52102,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:47:25.000Z","msg":"應該搵個師傅係屌到你飛起既 去到考試已經無壓力 因為之前俾人屌到百毒不侵 <br />\n不過我都明考牌個種壓力 身邊個個朋友一早考哂得自己未考 仲要洗咁多幾錢<br />\n利申：學咁多堂車俾個師傅屌足咁多堂  1take pass"},{"pid":"76852e688bf940a318efb9c248733c023eb1f099","tid":424923,"uid":89,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T23:54:31.000Z","msg":"肥左唔開心都正常<br />\n好老套咁講，唔洗灰心<br />\n比左錢又可以補考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗下自己衰咩同師傅講下<br />\n佢會比提醒你<br />\n出面搵其他人再補堂學下，比人屌下先會知自己衰咩<br />\n利申棍波考左2次合格（唔係學院考）"},{"pid":"58103c9ea8b5f1803abb6e3c92cea4fd53f6f908","tid":424923,"uid":82216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"完全明你感受 我都第三次先pass 但好彩衰過前兩次 宜家cut線完全冇難度<img src=\"/